00:35.327 --> 00:37.955
Honey, what have we always taught you?

00:37.955 --> 00:40.457
- Love who you are, as you are.
- Yes!

00:40.541 --> 00:42.125
Being comfortable in your skin

00:42.209 --> 00:43.961
